生 - #8</code><br />\n<blockquote>我黃到入心呀你老味，唔好再屈我五毛<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fclown.gif&h=b82ebc3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1645826/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1645826/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日拉咗好多未夠秤勇武，請各位小朋友退場 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>中學雞就返去讀書喇屌你老味，無撚晒理性。依家出面風向俾你班弱智仔搞死晒。四個月嚟既努力你班弱智仔搞死。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1631950/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1631950/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>放火燒鋪既都係臥底，「獅鳥」班仆街 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>邊個民居放火燒鋪，邊個就係鬼。我同班fd 發夢個陣見一個「獅鳥」一個。你老味係咪on撚9，我哋目標係對撚個政權，你同我搞鳩d平民民居？ 你班人on撚9架，燒撚死咗d 無辜平民，你係咪自焚賠返條命佢呀，你老味！！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1629178/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1629178/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/AwtAz1F.png\" />"},{"pid":"42f47bf69372bb3c5e18a94a8b302e201881f8dc","tid":2339152,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62677cc486cefb5c39c0395116d6e2be2e63f1b9","tid":2339152,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/SR8pJV2Z/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FSR8pJV2Z%2Fimage